<body>
    <h1>Hello Goodbye Function</h1>

    <p>
        Local functions can be declared in a Web page by using the
        &lt;script runat=&quot;server&quot;&gt; tag
    </p>

<ol>
<%
    string[] names = {"Name 1", "Name 2", "Name 3" };
    for(int i=0; i<names.Length; i++) {
		String message = sayGoodbye(names [ i ]);
%>	<li><%= message %></li>
<%	}
%>
</ol>

    <p>
        The text in the list above was generated by the following function
        declared in the Web page:
    </p>

    <pre>
&lt;script runat=&quot;server&quot;&gt;
    string sayGoodbye(string name)
    {
        return &quot;Goodbye &quot; + name;
    }
&lt;/script&gt;
    </pre>

    <h2>Source Code
    </h2>
